2009-11-25 Patrick M. Niedzielski <PatrickNiedzielski@gmail.com>

	* type.cpp: Type class implemented, can compile.  Added
	  macro for template classes implementing the Object/Type
	  system.

	* object.cpp: Object class implemented, can compile.

	* pointer.cpp: Pointer<T> class implemented.  Added various
	  typedefs to the class.  Removed non-const versions of
	  GetObject and GetPointer, because returning another
	  pointer or the dereferenced Object will in no way affect
	  the original Pointer<T>.

	* CMakeLists.txt: Added source files and install
	  information.

